List Rating Tables

cdec_rt_list.Rd

Get a list of all rating tables available through CDEC

cdec_rt_list(station_id = NULL)

Arguments

station_id

station for the location to get rating description for.

Examples

# list all rating tables in CDEC, you can use filter to search
cdec_rt_list()
#> # A tibble: 305 x 4
